<li>Thank you for always being my safe harbor.</li>
<li>You're the best mom a child could ask for.</li>
<li>Happy Mother's Day to my amazing Mom!</li>
<li>Your strength inspires me every day.</li>
<li>I'm eternally grateful for your love and guidance.</li>
<li>You are my everything, Mom.</li>
<li>Thank you for shaping me into the person I am today.</li>
